description:
Come on people. How can we let this BS happen? 
We can only stop this kind of totalitarian stuff happening if we unite and recognise what’s planned for us. How can we move into a better world for us and the future of humanity if we don’t know what it is we need to resist? We need some awareness of what’s really happening so we can overcome it! 
Do you want to have a health passport? Digital ID implanted in your body? Do you want you and everyone you know to be continually tracked and traced by the government? Me neither! 
What are we waiting for?!!
